  <official_title>A Phase 1, Open-label, Dose-escalation Study Of The Safety And Pharmacokinetics Of SNX-5422 Mesylate In Subjects With Refractory Solid Tumor Malignancies Or Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</official_title>
