  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hsp90 is a chemical in the body that is involved in promotion of cancer. SNX-5422 is an
      experimental drug that blocks Hsp90. It is being evaluated for safety and efficacy in
      patients with cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
