  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  &gt;18 years old

          -  histologically confirmed solid tumor malignancy

          -  refractory to available therapy or for which no therapy is available

          -  adequate organ function

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  CNS malignancy

          -  significant GI disease

          -  at risk for prolonged QT interval
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
